# Session [9] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Star Topology chist? (what is the star topology?)
- Tarze kar Star Topology  chejori hast? (how does stars topology work ?)
- Broadcast Domain dar Star Topology chist? (what is the braodcast domain in star topology?)

## Flashback – Star Basics
- Hame device ha be cable device markazi be ham vasl mishavand (mostly switch)  
- Har PC ye link joda ta markaz darad  

## Explanation

### Star Topology
- Device ha → be switch ya hub vasl mishavand  
- Age ye cable ghat beshe → faghat hamun device ghat mishe, baghie salem mimanan  
- Mashhoor tarin topology LAN ha  

### Broadcast Domain dar Star
- Ta vaghti switch estefade mishavad → **hame device ha yek broadcast domain hastand**  
- Broadcast az ye PC befresti, hame device haye dar LAN migiran  
- cable coaxial 8 reshte sim mesi ke harkodom az in sim ha 2 be 2 beham dige tapide shode 
- cable coazial faghat dar 100 metr kar mikone 

